Gatsby:
  - open source static website generator (SSG)
  - based on React 
  - Uses webpack 
  - Uses GraphQL

SSG: Static Site Generator 
  - Only files and folder 
  - no databases
  - no server-side rendering
  - no SQL injection if there is no db

Webpack:
  - Module bundler for JS 
  - puts everything in a dependency graph 
  - easier styling
  - code splitting
  - stable deploys
  - faster page load

Features:
  - 2-3 times faster than other sites
  - Open source 
  - easily transfer data

Steep learning curve